Investor Information





Sears Hometown and Outlet Store Investor Information

Sears Hometown and Outlet Stores, Inc., is a publicaly traded (NASDAQ: SHOS) national retailer primarily focused on selling home appliances, hardware, tools and lawn and garden equipment. We operate through two segments—the Sears Hometown and Hardware segment and the Sears Outlet segment.

