Wholesale Appliances - Sears Hometown Stores
Looking to buy appliances in bulk? Sears Hometown Stores offers wholesale discounts for bulk quantities of refrigerators, washers, dryers, and other types of appliances. Whether you're a contractor looking for bulk discounts or you're in charge of purchasing bulk quantities of appliances, we're here to make your job a breeze. If you'd like to get connected with one of our team members to customize your bulk buying request, please fill out the form below and let us know what you're looking for. Once your form is submitted, we'll have one of our representatives contact you in order to discuss your needs. We're looking forward to doing business with you!
